<body>
    <div class="page-overlay initial">
        <div class="loading-container">
            <div class="loading"></div>
            <div id="loading-text">tuning</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-top-extension"><h4>JYB</h4></div>
    <div class="menu-wrapper-nav">
        <div class="ham-stack ham-to-x  menu-toggle">
            <span class="ham"></span>
            <span class="ham"></span>
            <span class="ham"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <nav class="menu-wrapper">
        <ul class="menu-list">
            <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">Shows</a></li>
            <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">The Guys</a></li>
            <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">Gallery</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">History</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="social-share">
            <ul class="social-share-list ">
                <li><a class="social-link facebook"></a></li>
                <li><a class="social-link twitter"></a></li>
                <li><a class="social-link google-plus"></a></li>
                <li><a class="social-link youtube"></a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <div class="welcome-container" id="header">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="content-container col-md-8 col-lg-6">
                        <h1>The <span>Joel Young</span> Band</h1>
                        <ul class="desc-list list-inline">
                            <li>Country</li>
                            <li>Classic Rock</li>
                            <li>Variety</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>The Joel Young Band are a ragtag group of skillful musical philosophers who represent a broad cross-section of local musicians...</p>
                        <a href="/#about" class="btn btn-default scroll-to">Contact Us</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="logo-container col-md-4 col-lg-6">
                        <img src="~/images/logos/jyb-logo-425053-low-res.png" id="logo" class="initial" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-nav down"><a href="/#shows" class="scroll-to"><span class="fa fa-angle-down "></span></a></div>
        </div>

        @*::SHOWS SUMMARY CONTAINER::*@
        <div class="shows-summary-container" id="shows">
            @*<div class="scroll-nav up"><a href="/#header" class="scroll-to"><span class="fa fa-angle-up "></span></a></div>*@

            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 show-summary-desc">
                        <h2>JYB SHOWS</h2>
                        <div class="jyb-hr">
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                            Keep up to date with all JYB activity by subscribing to our Google calendar! Set a reminder so you won't miss the fun or any last
                            minute shows!
                        </p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-default btn-light">View Upcoming Shows</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-7">
                        <div class="polaroid" style="background-image:url('../../images/stage-mic.jpg')">
                            <p>The Stage is Set</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-nav down"><a href="/#about" class="scroll-to"><span class="fa fa-angle-down "></span></a></div>
        </div>

        @*::ABOUT CONTAINER::*@
        <div class="about-container" id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="polaroid" style="background-image:url('../../images/jyb-show.jpg')"></div>
                        <div class="absolute-image-placeholder"></div>
                        @*</div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">*@
                        <h2>JYB - BEHIND THE MUSIC</h2>
                        <div class="jyb-hr">
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                            Somewhere in between the demise of ButtonHead and the transformation of the multifaceted
                            Amarillo was the birth of The Joel Young Band! This band has consumed some of the most
                            seasoned countrified rockers in the Fort Wayne and surrounding areas. When ButtonHead
                            broke up in May of 2009, Amarillo was looking for a singer to replace Doug Holt. Doug
                            recently had a life-changing experience that wouldn't allow him to continue with Amarillo.
                            Joel was happy to step in. Amarillo played the next 6 months with Joel until they went
                            their separate ways that December. After a short stint with Big Fat Liar, Joel and the
                            rest of the guys (John Mazza, Gary McMeekin) decided to rebuild the band but wanted a
                            new name. After several weeks of debate, Scott Byler (previous drummer) suggested The
                            Joel Young Band... no one complained. So it was decided... The Joel Young Band was
                            born August 18th, 2010. (Appropriately,Joel's 43rd birthday) Since then, the band
                            has evolved into an eclectic group of musicians providing a broad range of talent.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>



<script src="~/Scripts/respond.min.js"></script>
<script src="~/Scripts/jquery-3.1.0.min.js"></script>
<script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="~/Scripts/lazysizes-core.js"></script>
<script src="~/js/ninja.js"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {

        setTimeout(function () {
            $(".page-overlay").removeClass("initial");
            $("#logo").removeClass("initial");
        }, 2000);

        $(".scroll-to").scrollToID(1000, -75);
        $(".menu-toggle").click(function () { toggleMenu(); })
        $(".page-overlay").click(function () { toggleMenu(); })
        $(".social-link").append("<span></span>");

        $(".facebook").attr("href", "http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=#http://www.joelyoungband.com");
        $(".twitter").attr("href", "http://www.twitter.com/");
        $(".google-plus").attr("href", "https://plus.google.com/");
        $(".youtube").attr("href", "http://www.youtube.com");

    });

    function toggleMenu() {
        $(".page-overlay").toggleClass("active");
        $(".menu-wrapper").toggleClass("active");
        $("main").toggleClass("active");
        $(".ham-stack").toggleClass("active");
    }

</script>